_header: All this world was full of grace
Bibliographic Ghosts: Oxford, Magdalen College Lat. 13, f. 2: not in this MS, nor Cambridge UK, Magdalene College 13 (F.4.13).
_description: Of the Nativity — six quatrains and Latin burden: ‘O O O O / Exultet mundus gaudio’

BLAdd40166c3.First Lines:
All this worlde was ful of graceWhen goddes son yborne
                    was…
BLAdd40166c3.Last Lines:
…Helpe vs to se god in the faceQuo sedet in
                    solacio
